    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_4157317199" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4157317199" />
    <a title="v" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/76558755-v"><img alt="v" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1594253473p2/76558755.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4157317199?book_show_action=true">Aug 11, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="v" class="user" itemprop="url" name="v" href="/user/show/76558755-v">v</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780307279446" href="/book/show/6021222-the-forever-war">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/76558755-v?shelf=own">own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/76558755-v?shelf=war-on-terror-etc">war-on-terror-etc</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4157317199" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11239389757070415190">Sharp, haunting, surreal, and floating, like the numbing camera feed of an AC-130, <i>The Forever War</i> is easily the best book I&apos;ve ever read about two wars that are just now finally over for now.</span>
  <span id="freeText11239389757070415190" style="display:none">Sharp, haunting, surreal, and floating, like the numbing camera feed of an AC-130, <i>The Forever War</i> is easily the best book I've ever read about two wars that are just now finally over for now.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11239389757070415190" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

