        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer40675554" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16274084537793031411">I can&apos;t remember who recommended this book, so I don&apos;t know who to thank...but I walked away from this book with my mouth open, shaking my head in awe.<br/><br/>This man can *write*. He brought scenes from war-ravaged countries into my living room, and found a way to accentuate both the devastation and the quiet small moments, creating a book that horrifies and educates and gives you hope, all at once.<br/><br/>Really, read this.</span>
  <span id="freeText16274084537793031411" style="display:none">I can't remember who recommended this book, so I don't know who to thank...but I walked away from this book with my mouth open, shaking my head in awe.<br /><br />This man can *write*. He brought scenes from war-ravaged countries into my living room, and found a way to accentuate both the devastation and the quiet small moments, creating a book that horrifies and educates and gives you hope, all at once.<br /><br />Really, read this.</span>
